Introducing SnekTab: Your ultimate browsing companion. Play the classic Snake game right on your new tab page for instant entertainment. Plus, effortlessly save and access your favorite URLs for lightning-fast browsing. Say hello to productivity and fun in one sleek extension.

By clicking "Add to Chrome" I accept and agree to install the SnekTab Chrome extension and hereby agree to set the Chrome New Tab to that provided by the service and the Privacy policy and Terms of Use.
The search results will be provided by Yahoo.
